---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About Fjord Labs | Board Game Accessories from Sweden"
  description="Fjord Labs is a small creative workshop in Sweden, designing and 3D-printing premium board game accessories."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-bark mb-8">
        About Fjord Labs
      </h1>

      <div class="prose-article">
        <p>
          Fjord Labs is a small creative workshop near a Swedish lake, surrounded
          by forest. We design and 3D-print board game accessories — resource
          tokens, score trackers, organizers, and component upgrades — for the
          games we love to play.
        </p>

        <p>
          Every product starts at our own game table. We play a game, notice
          what's clumsy about the stock components, and design something better.
          The Catan resource tokens exist because cardboard chits feel flat after
          your 50th game. The score tracker exists because we kept losing count
          mid-match. Everything we make solves a problem we've actually had.
        </p>

        <p>
          We also write the guides and articles on this site — rules
          clarifications, strategy tips, setup shortcuts — because we've spent
          hours in the same debates and searches that brought you here. If a page
          helps you settle an argument or improve your game, it did its job.
        </p>

        <h2>Where to Find Us</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="https://fjordlabs.etsy.com" target="_blank">Etsy Shop</a>
             — full product range, worldwide shipping
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
